*"Zadnja* stvar koju je ona napravila bila je da je poslala tu poruku." (The last thing she did was to send that message.)

*"Ona nikada ne zaboravlja *zadnje* pouke koje njen otac njoj govori." (She never forgets the last lessons her father tells her.)

*"U *zadnjoj* godini on je imao puno uspeha u školi." (In the last year he had a lot of success in school.)

*"On je spreman da učini sve u *zadnji* čas." (He is ready to do anything at the last minute.)

*"Ona je uzela *zadnju* šansu da se popravi." (She took the last chance to improve.)